most_recent.text: I’ve bought box after box lately that have turned out very dry and stales. They went right from the freezer at the store to my home freezer. Very disappointing. Have been buying the Walmart brand lately of there knock off uncrustable with not a problem as of yet.
most_recent.title: Terrible quality dry crustables

most_recent.text: One of the best brands making a peanut butter and jelly sandwich. Can’t go wrong
most_recent.title: Come on, it’s great like I knew it would be

most_recent.text: We had a snow/ice storm and it was really has. Before the storm, I went bought groceries because knew I would not be getting out for a while. I bought the strawberry uncrustable. My favorite go to snack. While snow ❄️ in the house. I went to eat one and the bread was hard and the peanut butter inside was crumbly. I thought maybe it was just that one, not the case all were the same. I was unable to return them to the store because I was snowed in. I was very disappointed because I have never experienced this with the uncrustable before.
most_recent.title: Bread was hard

most_recent.text: [This review was collected as part of a promotion.] I am such a huge fan of strawberry uncrustables. I can take them on the go and be ready for the day. These sandwiches thaw out so they can be eaten later while on the go. I like the fresh taste these offer. The jam and peanut butter have perfect consistency for that perfect snack or lunch. Great for the whole family. I already bought more.
most_recent.title: Great on the go

product_description.downstream_description: Just thaw, unwrap, and snack wherever you are! Uncrustables Peanut Butter & Strawberry Jam Sandwiches are a convenient, packable snack to take along wherever you and your kids are going next. This 15-count snack food pack comes with 15 single serve sandwiches that are individually wrapped for anytime snacking and have 6 grams of protein (5% DV) per serving (See Nutrition Information for Fat, Saturated Fat, and Sodium Content). These frozen grab-and-go sandwiches taste great and are full of peanut butter and strawberry jam flavor. For a true taste of home, kids and adults alike can simply grab an Uncrustables Peanut Butter & Strawberry Jam Sandwich to thaw and eat on-the-go. The convenient sandwich packs are great for lunch breaks, carpool rides, trips to and from little league, and so much more! They have no high fructose corn syrup, so go ahead and keep a couple boxes stocked in the freezer for when any snack time situation hits.
